---
title: Easy Cheesy Chicken & Oregano-Roasted Veggies with Pear Salad & Red Pesto Mayo
description: We can’t decide which we like best in this dish - the succulent spiced chicken, crunchy pear salad or oregano
roasted veggies topped with creamy pesto mayo. We’ll leave it up to you, but don’t be shy about agreeing that
every element is hard to beat.
